A member of the Bauchi State House of Assembly representing Baraza Dass constituency, Honourable Musa Mante was killed by suspected gunmen on Thursday night at his residence in Dass. The gunmen, suspected to be armed robbers, invaded his house at the late in the night. His wife was reportedly abducted by the gunmen. Hon. Musa had tested positive of COVID-19 some weeks ago and was recuperating at home. Details shortly…